case class perMinute(codeNum:String, date:String, time:String, price:Integer)

        .map(s=>perMinute(s(0),s(1),s(2),s(3).toInt))
        
case class stockInfo(codeNum:String, name:String)
val itemInfo = SI.map(s=>s.split(","))
        .map(s=>stockInfo(s(0),s(1)))
        
stock.toDF().registerTempTable("goingPrice")
itemInfo.toDF().registerTempTable("itemInfo")

        TO_DATE(CAST(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(date, 'yyyyMMdd') AS TIMESTAMP)) as DATE,
        from_unixtime(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(time, 'HHmm'),"HH:mm") as TIME,
        hour(CAST(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(time, 'HHmm') AS TIMESTAMP)) as HOUR,
        minute(CAST(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(time, 'HHmm') AS TIMESTAMP)) as MINUTE,
        price
from goingPrice where codeNum = "A000020"
